title: Cobie Smulders | Trump’s Rambling Phone Interview with Sean Hannity: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the president rambling in phone interviews while his administration threatens war with Iran the week after announcing his re-election bid.

Then, Cobie Smulders talks about Spider-Man: Far From Home, participating in a charity softball game and her upcoming television show Stumptown.

She also takes a few more questions backstage exclusively for the podcast.
